# Foods database

Per the stated portion. All macros in grams, kcal in kilocalories. Add the foods
you eat often so the coach looks them up instead of guessing — these rows are
just a generic starter set with standard values.

## Conventions

- `unit`: piece / 100g / tbsp / portion
- `per`: how many of that unit the row's macros are for
- Ate 50 g of a "per 100 g" row? multiply by 0.5

